title: 1935 Women's Western Open
text: The 1935 Women's Western Open was a <a href="golf">golf</a> competition held at <a href="Sunset%20Ridge%20Country%20Club">Sunset Ridge Country Club</a>, the 6th edition of the event. <a href="Opal%20Hill">Opal Hill</a> won the championship in <a href="match%20play">match play</a> competition by defeating <a href="Mrs.%20S.L.%20Reinhart">Mrs. S.L. Reinhart</a> in the final match, 9 and 7.
